# Vulnerability Prioritization Tool — API Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.
# None of these keys are required; they only increase rate limits and coverage.

# ── NVD API Key ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Increases NVD rate limit from 5 req/min → 5 req/sec (60x faster for large batches)
# Get your free key at: https://nvd.nist.gov/developers/request-an-api-key
# NVD_API_KEY=your_nvd_api_key_here

# ── GitHub Personal Access Token ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Increases GitHub Search rate limit from 10 req/min → 30 req/min
# Also enables Metasploit module detection via code search in rapid7/metasploit-framework
# Create a token (no special scopes needed for public data):
#   https://github.com/settings/tokens → "Generate new token (classic)" → no scopes required
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

